*+
*  Name:
*     ADP_CMN

*  Purpose:
*     Define ADP_ subroutine package common block

*  Language:
*     Starlink Fortran

*  Type of Module:
*     Global variables include file.

*  Description:
*     This file defines one global variable which is the ADP indentation
*     level. This variable should be defined to be zero on image startup 
*     by using an associated BLOCK DATA module.

*  Prior Requirements:
*     None.

*  References:
*     ADP Subroutine Guide : http://www.sr.bham.ac.uk/asterix-docs/Programmer/Guides/adp.html

*  Keywords:
*     package:adp, usage:public

*  Authors:
*     DJA: David J. Allan (Jet-X, University of Birmingham)
*     {enter_new_authors_here}

*  History:
*     21 Dec 1995 (DJA):
*        Original version.
*     {enter_changes_here}

*-

*  Global Variables:
      INTEGER                   ADP_INDENT		! Indentation level

*  Word aligned values      
      COMMON /ADP_CMN/          ADP_INDENT

*  Save common block contents
      SAVE /ADP_CMN/
*.
